msgid "Hostinger blog theme"
msgstr "Tema Blog Hostinger"

#. Description of the theme
msgid ""
"Hostinger Blog Theme is the perfect choice for bloggers seeking a powerful "
"yet lightweight solution. Built with SEO and mobile responsiveness in mind, "
"this theme ensures optimal performance and a better online presence. It "
"includes pre-made home, about us, contact us, and blog pages, giving your "
"blog a seamless and quick start. Regardless of your niche, take your blog to "
"the next level with this lightweight and professional-looking theme."
msgstr ""
"Ingin tema blog yang ringan dan serba ada? Tema Blog Hostinger jawabannya! "
"Tema ini sangat cocok digunakan oleh blogger yang ingin tema lengkap dan "
"ringan. Tema Blog Hostinger sudah teroptimasi SEO dan pastinya mobile "
"friendly. Performa dan kunjungan website dijamin optimal. Sudah termasuk "
"halaman utama, tentang kami, kontak, dan blog. Anda tidak perlu repot buat "
"blog dari nol. Bisa wujudkan berbagai ide hebat Anda dengan tampilan yang "
"menarik dan profesional."

